#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.random.standard_t.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.random.standard\\_t"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_t.standard_t:1 of
msgid ""
"Draw samples from a standard Student's t distribution with `df` degrees "
"of freedom."
msgstr "从具有 `df` 自由度的标准学生 t 分布中抽取样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_t.standard_t:4 of
msgid ""
"A special case of the hyperbolic distribution.  As `df` gets large, the "
"result resembles that of the standard normal distribution "
"(`standard_normal`)."
msgstr ""
"双曲分布的一个特例。当 `df` 变大时，结果类似于标准正态分布 (`standard_"
"normal`)。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_t.standard_t of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_t.standard_t:8 of
msgid "Degrees of freedom, should be > 0."
msgstr "自由度，应大于 0。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_t.standard_t:10 of
msgid ""
"Output shape.  If the given shape is, e.g., ``(m, n, k)``, then ``m * n *"
" k`` samples are drawn.  If size is ``None`` (default), a single value is"
" returned if ``df`` is a scalar.  Otherwise, ``mt.array(df).size`` "
"samples are drawn."
msgstr ""
"输出形状。如果给定的形状是，例如 ``(m, n, k)``，则抽取 ``m * n * k`` 个"
"样本。如果 size 是 ``None``（默认），当 ``df`` 是标量时返回单个值。否则，"
"抽取 ``mt.array(df).size`` 个样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_t.standard_t:15 of
msgid "Desired chunk size on each dimension"
msgstr "每个维度上期望的块大小"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_t.standard_t:17 of
msgid "Allocate the tensor on GPU if True, False as default"
msgstr "如果为 True，则将张量分配在 GPU 上，默认为 False"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_t.standard_t:19 of
msgid "Data-type of the returned tensor."
msgstr "返回张量的数据类型。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_t.standard_t of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_t.standard_t:22 of
msgid ""
"**out** -- Drawn samples from the parameterized standard Student's t "
"distribution."
msgstr "**out** -- 从参数化的标准学生 t 分布中抽取的样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_t.standard_t of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_t.standard_t:26 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_t.standard_t:27 of
msgid "The probability density function for the t distribution is"
msgstr "t 分布的概率密度函数为"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_t.standard_t:29 of
msgid ""
"P(x, df) = \\frac{\\Gamma(\\frac{df+1}{2})}{\\sqrt{\\pi df}\n"
"\\Gamma(\\frac{df}{2})}\\Bigl( 1+\\frac{x^2}{df} \\Bigr)^{-(df+1)/2}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_t.standard_t:32 of
msgid ""
"The t test is based on an assumption that the data come from a Normal "
"distribution. The t test provides a way to test whether the sample mean "
"(that is the mean calculated from the data) is a good estimate of the "
"true mean."
msgstr ""
"t 检验基于数据来自正态分布的假设。t 检验提供了一种方法来检验样本均值（即"
"从数据中计算出的均值）是否是对真实均值的良好估计。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_t.standard_t:37 of
msgid ""
"The derivation of the t-distribution was first published in 1908 by "
"William Gosset while working for the Guinness Brewery in Dublin. Due to "
"proprietary issues, he had to publish under a pseudonym, and so he used "
"the name Student."
msgstr ""
"t 分布的推导最早由威廉·戈塞特于 1908 年在都柏林的吉尼斯酿酒厂工作时发表。"
"由于产权问题，他必须使用笔名发表，因此他使用了“Student”这个名字。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_t.standard_t:43 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_t.standard_t:44 of
msgid "Dalgaard, Peter, \"Introductory Statistics With R\", Springer, 2002."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_t.standard_t:46 of
msgid ""
"Wikipedia, \"Student's t-distribution\" "
"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Student's_t-distribution"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_t.standard_t:50 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_t.standard_t:51 of
msgid ""
"From Dalgaard page 83 [1]_, suppose the daily energy intake for 11 women "
"in Kj is:"
msgstr ""
"根据 Dalgaard 第 83 页 [1]_，假设 11 名女性每日的能量摄入量（单位：千焦）"
"为："

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_t.standard_t:59 of
msgid ""
"Does their energy intake deviate systematically from the recommended "
"value of 7725 kJ?"
msgstr "她们的能量摄入是否系统性偏离推荐值 7725 千焦？"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_t.standard_t:62 of
#, python-format
msgid ""
"We have 10 degrees of freedom, so is the sample mean within 95% of the "
"recommended value?"
msgstr "我们有 10 个自由度，那么样本均值是否在推荐值的 95% 范围内？"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_t.standard_t:71 of
msgid ""
"Calculate the t statistic, setting the ddof parameter to the unbiased "
"value so the divisor in the standard deviation will be degrees of "
"freedom, N-1."
msgstr "计算 t 统计量，将 ddof 参数设置为无偏值，使得标准差中的除数为自由度 N-1。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_t.standard_t:79 of
msgid ""
"For a one-sided t-test, how far out in the distribution does the t "
"statistic appear?"
msgstr "对于单侧 t 检验，t 统计量在分布中出现的位置有多远？"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_t.standard_t:85 of
#, python-format
msgid ""
"So the p-value is about 0.009, which says the null hypothesis has a "
"probability of about 99% of being true."
msgstr "因此 p 值约为 0.009，这意味着原假设为真的概率约为 99%。"

